      "content": "\u003cdiv class\u003d\"introduction img-head\"\u003e\r\n  \u003cdiv class\u003d\"header\"\u003e\r\n   \u003cimg src\u003d\"data:image/svg+xml;base64,\" alt\u003d\"\"\u003e\r\n    \u003ch3\u003eTelco Churn Prediction - Data Studio\u003c/h3\u003e\r\n  \u003c/div\u003e\r\n\r\n  \u003csection\u003e\r\n    \u003ch4\u003eOverview\u003c/h4\u003e\r\n    \u003cp\u003e\r\n      This app helps telecom providers predict customer churn by analyzing transactional patterns and customer behavior using classification models.\r\n      It enables businesses to proactively identify at-risk customers and trigger retention strategies to reduce churn and improve satisfaction.\r\n    \u003c/p\u003e\r\n  \u003c/section\u003e\r\n\r\n  \u003csection\u003e\r\n    \u003ch4\u003eInput\u003c/h4\u003e\r\n    \u003cp\u003eUsers provide:\u003c/p\u003e\r\n    \u003cul\u003e\r\n      \u003cli\u003e\u003cspan\u003e+\u003c/span\u003e Filtered transactional data (via options such as International Plan, Voice Mail Plan, Churn Status)\u003c/li\u003e\r\n      \u003cli\u003e\u003cspan\u003e+\u003c/span\u003e Selected features (e.g., number of vmail messages, total minutes/calls across time bands, number of customer service calls, etc.)\u003c/li\u003e\r\n      \u003cli\u003e\u003cspan\u003e+\u003c/span\u003e Choice of model type (H2O or Spark ML)\u003c/li\u003e\r\n      \u003cli\u003e\u003cspan\u003e+\u003c/span\u003e Custom model name for training or validation\u003c/li\u003e\r\n      \u003cli\u003e\u003cspan\u003e+\u003c/span\u003e CSV data containing records for churn prediction\u003c/li\u003e\r\n    \u003c/ul\u003e\r\n  \u003c/section\u003e\r\n\r\n  \u003csection\u003e\r\n    \u003ch4\u003eOutput\u003c/h4\u003e\r\n    \u003cp\u003eThe app delivers:\u003c/p\u003e\r\n    \u003cul\u003e\r\n      \u003cli\u003e\u003cspan\u003e+\u003c/span\u003e Churn prediction classification model trained on user-selected features\u003c/li\u003e\r\n      \u003cli\u003e\u003cspan\u003e+\u003c/span\u003e Validation results of the trained modelâ€™s performance metrics\u003c/li\u003e\r\n      \u003cli\u003e\u003cspan\u003e+\u003c/span\u003e Predicted churn status for the uploaded dataset\u003c/li\u003e\r\n      \u003cli\u003e\u003cspan\u003e+\u003c/span\u003e Visualizations showing data distribution, churn patterns, and segment-level insights\u003c/li\u003e\r\n      \u003cli\u003e\u003cspan\u003e+\u003c/span\u003e Triggers for customer retention program initiation based on prediction results\u003c/li\u003e\r\n    \u003c/ul\u003e\r\n  \u003c/section\u003e\r\n  \r\n  \u003csection\u003e\r\n    \u003ch4\u003eBenefits\u003c/h4\u003e\r\n    \u003cul\u003e\r\n      \u003cli\u003e\u003cspan\u003e+\u003c/span\u003e Helps proactively identify and retain at-risk customers.\u003c/li\u003e\r\n      \u003cli\u003e\u003cspan\u003e+\u003c/span\u003e Can help reduce customer churn and improve customer lifetime value.\u003c/li\u003e\r\n      \u003cli\u003e\u003cspan\u003e+\u003c/span\u003e Enables marketing optimization and implementation of customer service efforts by targeting specific customer segments.\u003c/li\u003e\r\n    \u003c/ul\u003e\r\n  \u003c/section\u003e\r\n\u003c/div\u003e\r\n",
